OL,3,C'Don't risk safety' mayor tells bus
OL,4,Cdrivers as temperatures soar on
OL,5,Chottest day
OL,7,FSadiq Khan said bus drivers should not
OL,8,Frisk their personal safety after
OL,9,Ftemperatures soared in the summer
OL,10,Fheatwave.
OL,12,FThe mayor said drivers who think their
OL,13,Fbus is too hot "must stop" and not
OL,14,Fworry about following their usual
OL,15,Ftimetable.
OL,17,FITV News London has previously exposed
OL,18,Fshocking conditions including drivers
OL,19,Ffalling asleep at the wheel and forced
OL,20,Fto urinate in jars as well as working
OL,21,Fin hot cabs with little ventilation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
