OL,3,C'Don't risk safety' mayor tells bus
OL,4,Cdrivers as temperatures soar on
OL,5,Chottest day
OL,7,F"I've been concerned about bus drivers
OL,8,Ffor decades," Sir Sadiq said.
OL,10,F"I remember really well my dad telling
OL,11,Fme stories about 1976 and how awful it
OL,12,Fwas for him driving a bus.
OL,14,F"So I instructed TFL to contact every
OL,15,Fbus operator who run the buses to make
OL,16,Fsure they are examined, that the bus
OL,17,Fdrivers have a proper coolant system
OL,18,Finside the cabin, to make sure
OL,19,Fupstairs the coolant systems are
OL,20,Fworking.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782384482
OL,3,C'Don't risk safety' mayor tells bus
OL,4,Cdrivers as temperatures soar on
OL,5,Chottest day
OL,7,F"Also to say that the bus performance
OL,8,Findicators do not apply during this
OL,9,Fheat wave. I was concerned that bus
OL,10,Fdrivers may be worried they'll be
OL,11,Fpenalised for not following a strict
OL,12,Ftimetable.
OL,14,F"But also I've been quite clear that
OL,15,Fbus drivers who think their cabin is
OL,16,Ftoo hot or the bus is too hot must
OL,17,Fstop.
OL,19,F"They shouldn't risk their own
OL,20,Fpersonal safety are those of their
OL,21,Fpassengers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
