CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782384482
OL,3,C'Don't risk safety' mayor tells bus
OL,4,Cdrivers as temperatures soar on
OL,5,Chottest day
OL,7,FThe mayor said it was important to
OL,8,Flook after frontline workers, "whether
OL,9,Fyou're a bus driver, where you work in
OL,10,Fthe underground, you work on the
OL,11,FElizabeth Line, you work in the
OL,12,Foverground or any job across London,"
OL,13,Fhe added.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
